Cryptocurrency exchange reviews

As a cryptocurrency exchange aggregator, we at SwapSpace strive to provide our customers with offers only from the best crypto exchanges. To aid in the search for the best, we’ve decided to collect the community reviews for all the services that we list — straight from those people who’ve made an exchange. Our vision for this page is to help you make a better-informed choice on where to exchange your crypto, as well as to provide a platform for you to say something about your own experience.

Who can leave a review?

Only the users who have completed an exchange process. One customer can only add one review per exchange.

Why should I trust the reviews on this page?

We only accept reviews from the users who entered the valid exchange ID, i.e. the ones who have really swapped their crypto. Besides, an exchange can be reviewed only once, so that the users can’t cheat by leaving multiple comments or ranking the same exchange several times. In addition to this, we still screen the reviews, so even if something suspicious makes it through despite these measures, we will catch it.

Will the exchange service team see my review?

Yes, we alert the exchange representatives about the reviews they are getting. You can get a reply to your feedback from the exchange service team.
